milestones.description: Azhar Hossain has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (16) in an innings in ODIs for BAN, going past Minhajul Abedin's 8
Azhar Hossain's 54 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BAN), surpassing Minhajul Abedin's 40
John Wright and Martin Crowe's 158-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 152 between Glenn Turner and Bruce Edgar
Azhar Hossain and Gazi Ashraf's 26-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Gazi Ashraf and Faruque Ahmed
Azhar Hossain and Akram Khan's 52-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 31 between Gazi Ashraf and Athar Ali Khan
Aminul Islam and Enamul Haque's 40-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Athar Ali Khan and Akram Khan
Gazi Ashraf has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for BAN, going past Gholam Nousher
Enamul Haque has conceded the most runs in an innings (72) in ODIs for BAN, going past Gholam Nousher's record of 55
Azhar Hossain and Akram Khan's 52-run partnership is BAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 46 between Golam Faruq and Aminul Islam
